text: The Škoda Roomster is a car produced by Škoda Auto since 2006. There is panel van version of the Roomster. It is called the Praktik, which wasn't sold in the UK. Production stopped in 2015, as more people were buying the Yeti. == Engines == * 1.2 HTP 47 kW (64 hp) and 51 kW (69 hp) * 1.2 TSI 63 kW (86 hp) and 77 kW (105 hp) * 1.4 16V 63 kW (86 hp) * 1.6 16V 77 kW (105 hp) * 1.2 TDI 55 kW (75 hp) * 1.4 TDI 51 kW (69 hp) and 59 kW (80 hp) * 1.6 TDI 66 kW (90 hp) and 77 kW (105 hp) * 1.9 TDI 74 kW (100 hp) and 77 kW (105 hp) Roomster Category:2000s automobiles
title: Škoda Roomster
